#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.median.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.median"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:1 of
msgid "Compute the median along the specified axis."
msgstr "沿指定轴计算中位数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:3 of
msgid "Returns the median of the tensor elements."
msgstr "返回张量元素的中位数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:5 of
msgid "Input tensor or object that can be converted to a tensor."
msgstr "输入张量或可转换为张量的对象。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:7 of
msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which the medians are computed. The default is to "
"compute the median along a flattened version of the tensor. A sequence of"
" axes is supported since version 1.9.0."
msgstr ""
"计算中位数的轴。默认情况下沿张量的展平版本计算中位数。自版本 1.9.0 起支持"
"轴序列。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:11 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape and buffer length as the expected output, but the type (of the"
" output) will be cast if necessary."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。它必须具有与预期输出相同的形状和缓冲区长度，"
"但必要时会进行类型转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:15 of
msgid "Just for compatibility with Numpy, would not take effect."
msgstr "仅为了与 Numpy 兼容，不会生效。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:17 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the original `arr`."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则在结果中将被规约的轴保留为大小为一的维度。使用此选项时"
"，结果将能正确地与原始 `arr` 广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:22 of
msgid ""
"**median** -- A new tensor holding the result. If the input contains "
"integers or floats smaller than ``float64``, then the output data-type is"
" ``np.float64``.  Otherwise, the data-type of the output is the same as "
"that of the input. If `out` is specified, that tensor is returned "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"**median** -- 保存结果的新张量。如果输入包含小于 ``float64`` 的整数或"
"浮点数，则输出数据类型为 ``np.float64``。否则，输出的数据类型与输入相同。"
"如果指定了 `out`，则返回该张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mean`, :py:obj:`percentile`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:32 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.median.median:33 of
msgid ""
"Given a vector ``V`` of length ``N``, the median of ``V`` is the middle "
"value of a sorted copy of ``V``, ``V_sorted`` - i e., "
"``V_sorted[(N-1)/2]``, when ``N`` is odd, and the average of the two "
"middle values of ``V_sorted`` when ``N`` is even."
msgstr ""
"给定长度为 ``N`` 的向量 ``V``，``V`` 的中位数是其排序后副本 ``V_sorted`` "
"的中间值——即当 ``N`` 为奇数时的 ``V_sorted[(N-1)/2]``，以及当 ``N`` 为"
"偶数时 ``V_sorted`` 中间两个值的平均值。"

